		<td><b>Re: Future compo ideas</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I approve of the remix idea. It at least gives me an incentive to work with other source code bases, instead of tending to reinvent everything all the time.<br /><br />As the flash save functionality is worked out, the app compo would become more desirable. Being able to load and save data is kind of a requirement for computer like tools. For example, after working a bit with simple physics math I felt like I wanted to make a movement designing tool that runs in the NES.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


